  <description>
    <p>
      Q22 is a cross-platform binary file editor and hex editor, based on the
      original Catch22 HexEdit application for Windows.
    </p>
    <p>
      It supports direct binary editing, large files, bookmarks, search and
      navigation, import and export formats, file properties, string
      extraction, C-style structure inspection, and disassembly for common CPU
      architectures.
    </p>
  </description>

